{"tid":1939504,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友堅持要做兄弟","createTime":"2020-03-23T07:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T14:12:06.000Z","uid":11256,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ee023032cfd9961bae6419628576d31a34550e3","tid":1939504,"uid":11256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"我男朋友話佢個同事結婚<br />\n死都要去佢個婚禮同飲宴<br />\n話呢啲咁開心既日子一定唔會染病<br />\n我話你無睇過愉景灣單新聞咩?<br />\n佢話今次唔同嫁<br />\n我就屌佢，人地結婚關你咩事啊<br />\n本身去飲已經要比人情<br />\n仲要做兄弟自己比錢買禮服<br />\n我之前去朋友個啲婚宴<br />\n做兄弟仲有利是收啊<br />\n你係咪無腦啊？<br />\n佢勁嬲，嬲到話要同我分手<br />\n唉，依家可以點算？<br />\n如果唔去，仲洗唔洗比人情"},{"pid":"c02de88c40f3d18da4bd9972aa55cf8dbee28b3b","tid":1939504,"uid":51041,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n<br />\n依個時勢肯做兄弟既兄弟先係真兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d97d9dcf0885ef3b36bffd3fb2c3fc28f54f40","tid":1939504,"uid":129973,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:49:34.000Z","msg":"所有感情問題一律建議分手<br />\n你男朋友仲要係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁嘅時勢死要去飲<br />\n佢朋友都唔方好得去邊 延遲婚宴唔得咩？<br />\n到時齊齊中招真係恭喜哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a5b864a1c5f454e45ac31aab8c91109ed544a0","tid":1939504,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"14日唔好見, 解決"},{"pid":"eca9a01f10b905dfdfc61648c1b8a9e970c00338","tid":1939504,"uid":317485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好再推，這個帖子充滿謊話，犯了十誡。"},{"pid":"c14c3664c19bd89a910c9d8e3dcdbb28956c1ec9","tid":1939504,"uid":11256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2d97d9dcf0885ef3b36bffd3fb2c3fc28f54f40","tid":1939504,"uid":129973,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:49:34.000Z","msg":"所有感情問題一律建議分手<br